      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 fixture geometry and loading protocol directly replicate the COU (non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw, compression-bending). No extrapolation beyond the validated geometry or loading regime is claimed. Similarity argument documented in the V&V plan."
    }
