    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted based on documented scope limitation to quasi-static room-temperature loading consistent with the intended COU. All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96. The methodology described in the supporting peer-reviewed protocol (referenced via referencesIdentifier) underpins the uncertainty quantification workflow applied here. Overall credibility is assessed as sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence context.",
